InclusionRules.name: At least 1 Measurement of total cholesterol with value between 3.37-8.29 mmol/L (130-320 mg/dL) on or in prior 5 years of index
At least 1 Measurement of HDL cholesterol with between value 0.52-2.59 mmol/L (20-100 mg/dL) on or in prior 5 years of index
AT least 1 Measurement of systolic blood pressure with value between 90-200 mm Hg on or in prior 1 year of index
Have 0 condition occurrences of myocardial infarction, stroke (ischemic or hemorrhagic), heart failure, atrial fibrillation  all time on or prior to index
Have 0 procedures of percutaneous coronary intervention OR coronary artery bypass surgery all time on or prior to index
Have 0 condition occurrences of angina all time on or prior to index
Have 0 condition occurrence of ischemic heart disease all time on or prior to index
Have 0 condition occurrences of type 2 diabetes all time on or prior to index
Have 0 drug exposures of  drugs used for type 2 diabetes, non-insulin all time on or prior to index
Have 0 measurements of Hemoglobin A1c  >= 6.5 % all time on or prior to index
Have 0 drug exposures of  statins, all time prior to index and 30d post-index
